  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个医疗科技场景下的用户旅程时序图。核心流程是：用户在Frontend选择persona和phase，然后系统调用API v1，最终由Zyno这个LabAnalyzer组件来协调HealthTech_PatientRecords的数据处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Frontend",
        "API v1",
        "Zyno (HealthTech_LabAnalyzer)",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。Zyno是核心编排服务对吧？那API v1和Zyno之间的调用关系是同步的还是异步的？另外HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault在这里是什么角色，是存储还是安全网关？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API v1",
        "Zyno (HealthTech_LabAnalyzer)",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Zyno负责编排。API v1是同步调用Zyno的。HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault是合规的数据保险库，API v1在发起请求时需要在URL路径里带上它，比如POST /journeys/{vault}/step这样。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API v1",
        "Zyno (HealthTech_LabAnalyzer)",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "POST /journeys/{HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault}/step"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把四个参与者画出来：User、Frontend、API v1、Zyno。第一条消息是User到Frontend的\"Choose persona/phase\"，然后Frontend调用API v1的POST接口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Frontend",
        "API v1",
        "Choose persona/phase",
        "POST /journeys/{HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault}/step"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来API v1要触发Zyno的编排逻辑，标注为\"Orchestrate (HealthTech_PatientRecords)\"，强调Zyno会去协调患者记录服务。然后Zyno返回JourneyStepResponse，注意这个响应要关联回HIPAA_Vault。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API v1",
        "Zyno (HealthTech_LabAnalyzer)",
        "Orchestrate (HealthTech_PatientRecords)",
        "JourneyStepResponse (HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。Zyno返回的是虚线箭头给API v1，表示异步响应。然后API v1再返回给Frontend，内容是\"ui_blocks + next_state\"。最后Frontend渲染给用户。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Zyno (HealthTech_LabAnalyzer)",
        "API v1",
        "Frontend",
        "ui_blocks + next_state",
        "Render interactions"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，最后一步确认一下——API v1到Frontend的返回也是虚线吗？因为这是一个响应消息。还有，Zyno返回的JourneyStepResponse里带的HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault是表明数据合规来源对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API v1",
        "Frontend",
        "Zyno (HealthTech_LabAnalyzer)",
        "JourneyStepResponse (HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "对，两处返回都应该是虚线箭头。我刚才画API v1到Frontend时用了实线，需要改成虚线。另外确认Zyno返回的JourneyStepResponse括号里标注HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，表示这个响应是经过合规保险库验证的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API v1",
        "Frontend",
        "Zyno (HealthTech_LabAnalyzer)",
        "JourneyStepResponse (HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美。整个流程闭环了：用户选择→Frontend提交→API v1带Vault路径调用→Zyno编排患者记录→返回合规响应→Frontend渲染交互。这个时序图可以定稿了。",
